OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FThe cameraman who captured the moment
OL,7,Fin an incident that prompted
OL,8,Finternational outrage, has spoken of
OL,9,Fthe moment the man was killed "in
OL,10,Ffront of his eyes" to ITV News.
OL,12,FMohammed Abu Safia, a filmmaker and
OL,13,Fproducer who has been employed by ITV
OL,14,FNews to cover the war in Gaza, filmed
OL,15,Ffather of 14 Ramzi Abu Sahloul and a
OL,16,Fgroup of men waving a white flag after
OL,17,Fan evacuation order had been issued in
OL,18,Fdowntown Khan Younis.
