OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FThe footage he filmed around Mr Abu
OL,7,FSahloul's death prompted members of
OL,8,Fthe UK parliament .
OL,10,FMr Abu Safia explained to ITV News it
OL,11,Fwas Mr Abu Sahloul's family who had
OL,12,Furged him to publish the footage of
OL,13,Fthat day.
OL,15,F"This was one fact I was asked by his
OL,16,Fsons to report. They asked me to
OL,17,Fpublish the whole footage," Mr Abu
OL,18,FSafia said.
OL,20,F"When I interviewed them I sensed they
OL,21,Fwere still under shock," he added.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/18
