OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,F"All I see is death, destruction,
OL,7,Fshelling, diseases"
OL,9,FCamera operator Mr Abu Safia's life
OL,10,Fhas changed massively since the onset
OL,11,Fof full-blown conflict between Israel
OL,12,Fand Hamas on October 7.
OL,14,F"Before the war I used to wake up in
OL,15,Fthe morning, ride my bike to the
OL,16,Fbeach, have my coffee there, swim and
OL,17,Fget back by 7:30. My work starts at
OL,18,Fnine, I go to work, be back at home by
OL,19,F2pm to see my wife and my children, we
OL,20,Fhave our lunch and I may go to see my
OL,21,Ffriends, play cards."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/18
