OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FNow his days are very different.
OL,8,F"I go out at 6am, get back at 8pm,
OL,9,Fsometimes later at 10pm or 11pm. All I
OL,10,Fsee is death, destruction, shelling,
OL,11,Fdiseases, people complaining, . I see
OL,12,Fso many hardships and hear more sad
OL,13,Fstories, it makes it hard for me to
OL,14,Fsleep.
OL,16,F"I stay awake till 1am or 2am unable
OL,17,Fto sleep. I try hard to relax. But
OL,18,Fwhat I have seen keeps me up for days.
OL,19,FThis is very difficult and so hard for
OL,20,Fme to bear with."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/18
