OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,F"I sensed I shouldn't be where these
OL,7,Fcivilians were"
OL,9,FOn January 22 Mr Abu Safia had been
OL,10,Fdocumenting the experience of pregnant
OL,11,Fwomen and premature babies in the
OL,12,Farea, when he saw plumes of heavy
OL,13,Fblack smoke and civilians fleeing.
OL,15,F"I was on the exit of Al-Aqsa
OL,16,FUniversity when a man spoke English to
OL,17,Fme," Mr Abu Safia said, explaining
OL,18,Fthat as he was working for a Western
OL,19,Fnews outlet he decided to interview
OL,20,Fthe man.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/18
