OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FA few metres away he saw a group of
OL,7,Fmen, one of whom was raising a white
OL,8,Fflag.
OL,10,F"I approached them slowly, I was
OL,11,Fcautious. I reviewed the map to see if
OL,12,Fit was a safe place where I was or
OL,13,Fnot. I didn't want to put myself in
OL,14,Fany danger," Mr Abu Safia explained.
OL,16,F"I sensed I shouldn't be where these
OL,17,Fcivilians were," he added.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/18
