OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FOne of the civilians explained he and
OL,7,Fhis family had been forced out of
OL,8,Ftheir homes by the IDF the previous
OL,9,Fday.
OL,11,FHe said he was waiting at the closest
OL,12,Fpoint to the IDF trying to tell them
OL,13,Fthere were still civilians trapped in
OL,14,Fthe house he had come from, as they
OL,15,Fwere unable to follow evacuation
OL,16,Forders.
OL,18,F"It was a direct shot to his heart"
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/18
