OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FMilitary vehicles circled nearby as Mr
OL,7,FAbu Safia spoke to the man, and he
OL,8,Fnoticed a laser beam coming from the
OL,9,Fgun of a nearby sniper.
OL,11,F"I heard a sniper's gun fire. That was
OL,12,Fthe only fire noise. I stopped
OL,13,Frecording, and I was wondering if I
OL,14,Fwas in danger or if it was a warning
OL,15,Ffiring," he said.
OL,17,F"I realised then the man was shot."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G8/18
