OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FMr Abu Safia stopped recording for
OL,7,Faround five seconds after hearing the
OL,8,Fgunfire, but decided he needed to
OL,9,Fdocument what was happening, so began
OL,10,Frecording again.
OL,12,F"I approached slowly to see what
OL,13,Fhappened to the man. I saw how the man
OL,14,Fwas shot in his heart. His sons came
OL,15,Fto him to take him. They tried to
OL,16,Fcarry him, we were fired at again," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G9/18
