OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,F"It happened at 3.14pm. They were
OL,7,Fpeaceful, raising a white flag, all of
OL,8,Fthem raising their IDs. That man was
OL,9,Fraising his hands. When I approached
OL,10,Fhim to interview him his hands were
OL,11,Fup. Clearly he was peaceful. I don't
OL,12,Fknow why he was targeted."
OL,14,F"I wasn't scared because in my mind I
OL,15,Fthought it was a safe place. It wasn't
OL,16,Fa place where we were asked to
OL,17,Fevacuate," he added.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G10/18
