OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FRishi Sunak and the US were quizzed
OL,7,Fover an ITV News video which shows a
OL,8,Fcivilian being shot dead while in a
OL,9,Fgroup carrying a white flag in Gaza,
OL,10,Fmany say this shows a 'war crime,'
OL,11,FJohn Irvine and Robert Moore report
OL,13,F"If they wanted us to leave they
OL,14,Fshould've aimed in the air to warn us
OL,15,Fand make us leave. They didn't do
OL,16,Fthat. The man was shot before my eyes.
OL,17,FThey tried to save him but couldn't.
OL,18,FIt was a direct shot to his heart."
OL,20,FMr Abu Safia continued to record what
OL,21,Fwas happening on his camera.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G11/18
