OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,F"I didn't know what I should do,
OL,7,Fshould I run away or keep
OL,8,Fdocumenting?" he said. He didn't feel
OL,9,Fhe was able to help the victim as he
OL,10,Fdid not have any medical training.
OL,12,FThe group briefly took cover in Al-
OL,13,FAqsa University and created a
OL,14,Fmakeshift stretcher from a door. They
OL,15,Fthen carried the man to a bus as they
OL,16,Fwere unable to call for an ambulance
OL,17,Fand he was taken to a hospital.
OL,19,F"They were still under shock"
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G12/18
