OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FMr Abu Safia wanted to find out more
OL,7,Fabout what he had seen that afternoon.
OL,9,F"I tried to find the man's family. I
OL,10,Fkept looking for them for the whole
OL,11,Fday until I found them. It was clear
OL,12,Fhow much this man was loved by his
OL,13,Fpeople," he said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G13/18
