OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FHe, who was with his father when he
OL,7,Fwas shot. He said the family had
OL,8,Fcalled the ICRC (International
OL,9,FCommittee of the Red Cross) the night
OL,10,Fbefore the incident to report Israeli
OL,11,Ftanks were on their doorstep and there
OL,12,Fwere people who could not follow the
OL,13,Fevacuation orders.
OL,15,FThe son of the man who was shot dead
OL,16,Fwhile holding a white flag in Gaza has
OL,17,Fspoken to ITV News after the fatal
OL,18,Fattack, as Senior Correspondent John
OL,19,FIrvine reports
