OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FMr Abu Safia switched off after the
OL,7,Finterview, and didn't communicate with
OL,8,Fanyone for the rest of the day.
OL,10,F"I shared the footage with ITV News. I
OL,11,Fonly communicated with them to share
OL,12,Fwith them more details like his name
OL,13,Fand his story, and then I turned off
OL,14,Fmy phone to ease my stress from what I
OL,15,Fwitnessed. And here I am," he said.
OL,17,F"It was a crime. It happened that I
OL,18,Fwas there to document that crime. It
OL,19,Fwas in Al-Mawasi, it was supposed to
OL,20,Fbe a safe place," he said.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G15/18
