OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,FSo many people die everyday who have
OL,7,Fnothing to do with the war, Mr Abu
OL,8,FSafia said, and he has seen many
OL,9,Fhorrific scenes in his time working as
OL,10,Fa cameraman in Gaza.
OL,12,F"One of the most difficult things I've
OL,13,Fwitnessed is when someone dies before
OL,14,Fseeing the light. When a pregnant
OL,15,Fmother is killed and her foetus dies
OL,16,Fbefore seeing light. And the premature
OL,17,Fdeliveries because of the polluted air
OL,18,Fin displacement or because of mothers'
OL,19,Fundernourishment.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G    G16/18
