OL,3,CITV News cameraman who filmed man with
OL,4,Cwhite flag shot dead in Gaza speaks out
OL,6,F"It is a bad, difficult, scary, ," he
OL,7,Fadded.
OL,9,FMore than 26,000 Palestinians have now
OL,10,Fbeen killed in the conflict, the
OL,11,FHealth Ministry in Hamas-run Gaza said
OL,12,Fon Friday, and more than 64,000 people
OL,13,Fhave been wounded.
OL,15,FThe International Court of Justice
OL,16,F(ICJ) Israel must take all measures
OL,17,Fwithin its power to prevent genocide
OL,18,Fin Gaza, as requested in South
OL,19,FAfrica's original complaint.
